# Vercel deploys the Next.js portal at `04-the-final-portal/portal/`,
# bundling the milesymedia static files into its public/ via the
# build-portal.mjs prebuild step. Per-client portals at
# `04-the-final-portal/clients/<slug>/` deploy as SEPARATE Vercel
# projects (one per Live client), each with rootDirectory pinned to
# their own folder — this file isn't read for those.

# Reference codebases — not part of any deployment.
01 development/
02 felicias aqua portal work/
03 old portal/

# Per-client portals — each is a separate Vercel project.
# Excluded from the main portal deploy so its bundle stays small.
04-the-final-portal/clients/

# Local + build artefacts.
node_modules/
.next/
.data/
.vercel/
